Fetch Module Code

Source: R/ASM_Server.R
ASM_fetch_code.Rd

Fetches the code to generate results seen in the app

Usage

ASM_fetch_code(state)

Arguments

state

ASM state from ASM_fetch_state()

Value

NULL the ASM module does not generate code

Examples

# Creating a state object for testing
sess_res = ASM_test_mksession(session=list())
